Edition:
Quote:   ... this haunting spirit, or phantom, <i>(Kehua,)</i> which haunted its former place of residence, when in the body, ... differed widely from the sensible intellectual spirit <i>(Wairua)</i>, which had departed to the <i>reinga</i> and which was not feared.
Notes:  (Colenso Maori races)

